page_title: Alan - The Sommelier of Sandwich Makers
aduiance:
Private group  · 3 membersThe head Sous Chef, Alan, is nothing less than an artist.  2 pieces of bread are his canvass and assorted meats & vinegar his paint.  Speaking of the rustic vinaigrette, (which according to Alan should be applied to every sandwich in conjunction with lettuce), there is surely no finer then in the very rolling hills of Italy where it is mined.  The mood enhancing ambiance is amplified by the fluorescent lighting and very long lunch-rush lines.  This may indeed be the only SafeWay which should be recommended for at least three Michelin Stars.
   
   So, come to the Safeway Sandwich center.  The vinaigrette is flowing.  Every sandwich is a Tuscan Chicken.  And the bacon is *always* cooked.|Private group  · 3 members
